release.description:
Release notes can be found [on GitHub](https://github.com/projectcalico/calico/blob/v3.28.2/release-notes/v3.28.2-release-notes.md)

Attached to this release are the following artifacts:

- `release-v3.28.2.tgz`: container images, binaries, and kubernetes manifests.
- `calico-windows-v3.28.2.zip`: Calico for Windows.
- `tigera-operator-v3.28.2.tgz`: Calico Helm v3 chart.
- ocp.tgz: Manifest bundle for OpenShift.

Additional links:

- [VPP data plane release information](https://github.com/projectcalico/vpp-dataplane/blob/master/RELEASE_NOTES.md)
